Package it.polimi.LM39.model.leaderobject

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LeaderRequestedObjects
    class (can't be abstract because RuntimeAdapterFactory needs a concrete class) that will be extended by all leader requested objects
    RequestedCard
    To activate this leader you need *cardQty* cards of type *cardType*
    RequestedCardPointsResources
    To activate this leader you need *cardQty* cards of type *cardType*, *resources* resources and *points* points
    RequestedPoints
    To activate this leader you need *points* points
    RequestedResources
    To activate this leader you need *resources* resources
    RequestedSameCard
    To activate this leader you need *cardQty* cards of every type
    RequestedTwoCards
    To activate this leader you need *cardQty* cards of type *cardType* and *cardQty2* cards of type *cardType2*
